Name: UNE Gold Ingot (Flawed)
Description: A gold ingot cast by the United Nations of Earth (UNE) that is rated as being in flawed condition. These ingots were used in areas of the UNE where technological issues often hampered secure and instant money transfers. This rare item features the a worn three ring, six star logo used by the UNE within a circular recess and an elaborate, textured pattern across the rest of it.
